```_hsq.push(['trackEvent'], {
  id: 'Accessed Resource - ' + resource.title
});```
But the events aren't showing up in the reports or in the contacts I've used to test. These events are triggered by clicking on a link, so maybe it doesn't get registered before the window navigates to the next page? That's all I can think of. Anyone have any idea what I might be doing wrong with this, or how to fix it? Or some other way I could track this so I can trigger some workflows?
